Paulo, Garulhos, park near airport terminal, 19.viii.2000, EvN no 2000133 [rearing number], leafmines on unidentified 
<taxonomicName id="2BE96642B3D340976805D91AE2AA86AF" family="Myrtaceae" genus="Microlepidoptera" lsidName="Microlepidoptera" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" rank="family">Myrtaceae</taxonomicName>
